Database Password: The password was left as the default because we could not figure out how to change it without locking ourselves out of the database.

--- GENERAL LAYOUT ---

Welcome Page: index.html
    Clicking on the "Shop All" button directs the user to the product table page.

Products Page: main.html
    Requirement #1: This page uses two servlets to generate the product info in the table and a table of recently viewed products.
    Clicking on an image of the product directs the user to that product page. Under all the products is a "Recently Visited" section, which lists the last 5 seen products. There is also a link which leads to the shopping cart page.

Product Detail Page: product.html
    Requirement #2: This page also uses a servlet to query the database to generate the product details. If the user clicks the "Add to Cart" button, the session will save the product in the shopping cart. There is also a link which leads the user to the shopping cart page.

Check out Page: cart.html
    Requirement #3: This page displays the products ordered by the user and places the user's information into the database.
    Not implemented yet: Clicking the check out button places the order in the database.

